<b>RENT:</b> $2275/Month | <b>SIZE:</b> 671 sq ft | <b>BEDROOMS:</b> 1 | <b>BATHROOMS:</b> 1<br><br><b>LEASE TERMS:</b> 12-Month<br><br><b>Upstairs 1 bedrooms are $100 off for the first 6 months!</b><br><br><hr><b>ABOUT COMMUNITY: </b><hr><ul>You are invited to enjoy a comfortable and carefree lifestyle at the beautiful Cinnamon Ridge Apartments in Fullerton, CA. Our conveniently located community offers a variety of spacious one and two bedroom apartments for rent. Our apartments feature beautiful views, abundant sunlit windows, and private patios and balconies. Surrounded by lush landscaping, you can relax next to a tree or gather with friends at one of our conveniently located gas barbecue areas. Our community also features a sparkling swimming pool and the chance to unwind in our warm, bubbling spa. Cinnamon Ridge Apartments provide the perfect sanctuary. When it is time to leave the peaceful grounds, you can enjoy the surrounding area, featuring fine dining and entertainment all within walking distance from your home. Cinnamon Ridge is located within the Sunny Hills School district, and is minutes to CSUF. Our convenient location, comfortable apartments and friendly community management team will ensure your Fullerton apartment living experience is unmatched. Give us a call or stop by for your personalized tour to discover your new Fullerton apartment home at Cinnamon Ridge Apartments.<br><br>Pet Policy: Cats, Birds and Reptiles Allowed: Max 2 pets total per apartment. $500 Deposit. $35 Monthly Pet Rent. 2 Pet Limit.</ul><hr><b>UNIT FEATURES: </b><hr> <ul> ➢ Cable TV Ready<br>➢ Dishwasher<br>➢ Heating and Air Conditioning<br>➢ Private Patios &amp; Balconies<br>➢ Spacious Floor Plans<br>➢ Vaulted Ceilings (Upstairs Residences)<br>➢ Vertical Blinds<br></ul><hr><b>COMMUNITY FEATURES:</b><hr> <ul>➢ 24 Hour Laundry Facilities<br>➢ Controlled Access Gates<br>➢ Covered Carports with Storage<br>➢ Enclosed Garages Available<br>➢ Community Clubhouse with TV, Living &amp; Dining Areas<br>➢ On-Site Management &amp; Maintenance<br>➢ Professional Landscaping<br>➢ Swimming Pool and Spa<br></ul><hr><b>CONTACT US TODAY!</b><hr><br><big><b>Cinnamon Ridge</b></big><br>1421 N Gilbert St <br> Fullerton, CA 92833<br><br><b>Phone: </b> <a href="#" class="show-contact" title="click to show contact info" data-href="/reply/orc/apa/7516515818/__SERVICE_ID__" rel="nofollow">show contact info</a>
